  65. ‌let rec update_mod_field modu i shape n =
  66.   match shape with
  67.   | Function | Lazy ->
  68.      Obj.set_field modu i n
  69.   | Value _ ->
  70.      () (* the value is already there *)
  71.   | Class ->
  72.      assert (Obj.tag n = 0 && Obj.size n = 4);
  73.      let cl = Obj.field modu i in
  74.      for j = 0 to 3 do
  75.        Obj.set_field cl j (Obj.field n j)
  76.      done
  77.   | Module comps ->
  78.      update_mod_block comps (Obj.field modu i) n

  80. and update_mod_block comps o n =
  81.   assert (Obj.tag n = 0 && Obj.size n >= Array.length comps);
  82.   for i = 0 to Array.length comps - 1 do
  83.     update_mod_field o i comps.(i) (Obj.field n i)
  84.   done
